---
title: Spanish Chorizo Burger with Chimichurri Salad, Feta Aioli and Sweet Potato Wedges
description: This juicy chorizo burger gets slathered with chimichurri, feta mayo, and stuffed with spicy jalapenos! Spiced sweet potato wedges are the perfect side for this Spanish-inspired dinner!
